00:56:05,420 --> 00:56:07,490
"Ibu mertua"? Astaga.

956
00:56:07,559 --> 00:56:11,099
Seakan-akan ibu mertuanya mau memasakkannya ayam.

957
00:56:11,160 --> 00:56:12,799
Aku sudah senang jika dia tidak mengomel.

958
00:56:13,069 --> 00:56:16,339
Dia mengomel? Apa maksudmu?

959
00:56:16,440 --> 00:56:19,269
