00:56:25,539 --> 00:56:27,450
Makan pelan-pelan, nanti kamu tersedak.

962
00:56:27,509 --> 00:56:29,220
Santai saja.

963
00:56:40,089 --> 00:56:41,259
Bu.

964
00:56:55,009 --> 00:56:56,380
Ibu sedang apa?

965
00:56:56,440 --> 00:56:58,740
